{"tid":2488447,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子反國安法遊行非法集結罪成 羅德泉今判處監禁3個月","createTime":"2021-04-14T08:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T09:46:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a942813d2c18dcb13bbf311986064cf16d5c6d60","tid":2488447,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:45:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15030&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvpo9Jm%2BrpizTNr1X5Fgg%2Fao%3D&h=519986df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15030</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#羅德泉主任裁判官<br />\n#20200524銅鑼灣<br />\n#判刑<br />\n<br />\n陳 (29)  🛑已還押16日<br />\n<br />\n控罪：參與非法集結<br />\n被控於2020年5月24日，在銅鑼灣軒尼詩道與怡和街交界連同其他身分不詳人士參與非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n索取背景報告正面，被告同意內容。辯方律師呈上一封由李姓牧師撰寫新求情信，表示被告在收押時有深切反省，並希望修讀神學，將來貢獻社會。<br />\n<br />\n🔥判刑速報<br />\n即時監禁3個月❗️❗️"},{"pid":"883177c9f89401d378831630c0fbf0c6f681656d","tid":2488447,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26342c0d8263136ef2dc4b9e4de30d2d3ad1ab0f","tid":2488447,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff35ef190fc8521314a9046525b717efd9f16e1","tid":2488447,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcdee62ea4aa44553324df8e3da659a3cd1787e8","tid":2488447,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:58:28.000Z","msg":"羅狗"},{"pid":"542568048aa72bf5ae67f49441ff75374cd1f827","tid":2488447,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da7ec68127daf0faa1a5e7b2c5d0b5a5b66f509","tid":2488447,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:09:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b7a7a55cb6d79bd7af65f7cd3bc4e85798681c","tid":2488447,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:38:46.000Z","msg":"主任裁判官羅德泉指被告在集結行動中雖然不是主導者，但仍屬主要角色，因集結可以團結力量，壯大聲勢，令在場人士情緒高漲，而有膽量作出平常不敢做的行為。羅官指，根據片段被告只是「四圍行，無掟嘢」，在考慮所有情況後以4個半月作量刑起點，認罪扣減3分1刑期，今於東區裁判法院判被告即時監禁3個月。<br />\n<br />\n羅官表示，本案的集結不是單獨事件，並非與其他地方的集結案無關。現場人士集結在一起，一同起哄及聲勢浩大，以達到協同目的，有膽量作出堵路及破壞等行為；另指案發當日灣仔及銅鑼灣一帶有嚴重保安問題，有人堵路及縱火等。羅官續指，此類案件被告多為年輕人，大多沒有刑事案底，但仍屬重要角色，因為如果集結人士不出席聚集，即使號召者再努力仍難以成事。"},{"pid":"cfc9f6ae7fb8279b737cdaa34d25bc65536a40bf","tid":2488447,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:46:38.000Z","msg":"主任裁判官羅德泉指，雖然被告不是集結的主導者，但參與者也是重要角色，又指「集結主要在聲勢浩大下，參與者情緒高漲做出一啲平日唔敢做嘅事情」，如堵路等暴力行為；<span class=\"red\">若沒有他們出席，「號召者點努力都難以成事</span>」。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/5-24-%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-29%E6%AD%B2%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE%E5%B7%A5%E8%AA%8D%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%A3-3-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E8%A3%81%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%98-%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E8%80%85%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2/\" data-sr-u